            <thetext>Popup autoHide property does work, example: popup list from qx.ui.form.ComboBoxEx

On the other hand, autoHide property for non-modal windows does not work.
Example: search dialog from qx.ui.form.ComboBoxEx.

Procedure for reproducing the bug:

1) Open http://demo.qooxdoo.org/html/example/ComboBoxEx_1.html demo
2) Double click the combo for forcing the search dialog to appear
3) Click outside the dialog and nothing happens.  I expect the dialog to disappear.</thetext>
